Package: qgarch
Type: Package
Title: Quadratic GARCH-in-Mean Models for Volatility Feedback
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Sanghyun", family = "Hong",
           email = "sanghyun.hong@canterbury.ac.nz",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Fits QGARCH-in-mean models motivated by Campbell and Hentschel
    (1992) and the supplied replication scripts. The package implements the
    QGARCH-M(1,1) specification with four variants: lambda fixed at zero,
    lambda restricted to a function of the other parameters, lambda estimated
    freely, and a threshold extension with lambda varying by an indicator.
    The Markov-switching extension is intentionally omitted.
